{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script provides:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Quick sidechain routing from selected tracks to the track under the mouse.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Default setup of a 3/4 sidechain with corresponding 3/4 L\\R pins for input.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Usage:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab Select multiple tracks.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab Hover over a target track.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab A window will display available plugins.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 4.\tx360\tab Click "Create New Channel" after selecting a plugin to auto-create the next available send. For instance, if 3/4 is occupied, it will select 5/6, and if 5/6 is occupied, it will select 7/8, and so on.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 5.\tx360\tab Clicking "Yes" will route the send to the current sidechain pins of the selected plugin.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Language Support:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab English and Russian.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Toggle language by changing "local language = 'eng'" to 'ru' for Russian.\sa180\par}
